* ''Journalist of the Year'' at the [[Stonewall Awards]], 2009<ref>{{cite news |title=Independent journalist wins Stonewall award |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/press/independent-journalist-wins-stonewall-award-1816698.html |work=The Independent |date=7 November 2009 |accessdate=7 November 2009 | location=London}}</ref>
