* [[Amnesty International]] Newspaper Journalist of the Year in 2007<ref name="autogenerated2006"/>
* 'Young Journalist of the Year' at the [[British Press Awards]] in 2003<ref name=pg>{{cite web|title=British Press Awards: Past Winners|url=http://www.pressgazette.co.uk/story.asp?storycode=39598|publisher=''[[Press Gazette]]''|accessdate=17 April 2012}}</ref>
* 'Student News Journalist of the Year' by [[The Times]] in 2000<ref>{{cite news| first=Sally | last=Morris | work=The Times | title=Future Perfect | date=15 June 2000}}</ref>

